# macOS / Windows / editor junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.vscode/
.idea/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# Safety net: never commit a manager's real data to this repo.
#
# If you clone this repo and test the setup inside it, the assistant
# will create filled-in coach files named after your actual coach
# (coach-smith-profile.md). Those contain real names, emails, and
# phone numbers. The rules below keep them out of git.
#
# The NAME templates are explicitly allowed back in.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

coach-*-profile.md
coach-*-schedule.md
!templates/coach-NAME-profile.md
!templates/coach-NAME-schedule.md

# GotSport schedule exports — contain team, venue, and contact data.
# These belong in your working folder, never in the repo.
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.xls

# Filled-in personal files, if you ever work inside a clone.
# Templates live in templates/ and are tracked; copies elsewhere are not.
/user-profile.md
/manager-config.md
/scheduling-tracker.md
/manager-messaging-templates.md
